                                <li><b>Senapattinam, Tandrampattu Taluk, Tiruvanamalai., Tamilnadu:</b><br>20 homelights systems and 5 street lights. Expected date July 2018.</li>

                            </ol><br>The Liter of light project will be featured on our google chrome extension periodically and also on all future tech products so that they can receive adequate funding, reach and global support that they require to make
